{"tid":118981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴絲幾耐執一次房？","createTime":"2017-02-13T11:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T13:22:34.000Z","uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"535690530f20dd482f65c4d5550a360525a68bb6","tid":118981,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"睇到隔離巴打貼個書枱房相有感而發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己勁懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到頂唔順個日先會執房<br />\n枱會好小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要用個陣就會執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我身邊女仔fd都都同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係我地有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日執房/枱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂唔順先執<br />\n<br />\n或者分享下點樣可以保持整潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申好無手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282b0e9f0894e1922cf209892fe346293b243b12","tid":118981,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"還可怎麼爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958cb8e89b15368f8a6dc53895b470f5eaa49300","tid":118981,"uid":11417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55d043e448f62cfcf20af302f9a6d8bd6f13bd61","tid":118981,"uid":3356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"無房"},{"pid":"e2292216ea7fd82ee6a850038ebec4ab9ae8a5a6","tid":118981,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還可怎麼爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投契極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936c70a27d718cecdaac4cbce55e3d1680110c7a","tid":118981,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月 去到自己頂唔順就會執</blockquote><br />\n我最誇張試過成床都係衫<br />\n3個月無執過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9a0270a1730e4a2fe5a1c678a657e1b08bf571","tid":118981,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無房</blockquote><br />\n咁有枱咖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5488f78d76f48107815e47fc90fd1a4bdb09d18c","tid":118981,"uid":877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:01:52.000Z","msg":"十年都有 黎緊搬屋終於要執"},{"pid":"39e098c1c1393d68b0790152800647f5f5a6343d","tid":118981,"uid":13545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>還可怎麼爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投契極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得不到世人的允許"},{"pid":"899727f7d931ebd57d9e669e51d29b1aefead781","tid":118981,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"頂唔順先執<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：每一日都會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c6e8c650517488e137dc7a1a6982e62ede4baf","tid":118981,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>還可怎麼爭取<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投契極