ike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"逢星期日洗衫果執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ccc354a5248bde62162eb4bd499dfddf3b7f86","tid":118981,"uid":48800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頂唔順先執<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：每一日都會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你每日會花幾多時間執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實每日都係十至十五分鐘<br />\n因為每日都執 基本上唔會太亂"},{"pid":"076f58c61671dd053e66aef23443ee5d265018db","tid":118981,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"一個星期兩三次 十幾日大執抹figure"}]}